latestPosts.caption: being able to keep my posts unfiltered and making my winters feel like summer has been the biggest win of my life, idc if it is immature but i will say it out loud. always counting my blessings and never the stamps on my passport. one of the very few posts where i talk about what real achievement means to me. travelling has truly been a privilege in my life. and i love keeping my life low-key and not posting about my life constantly, the content at heart surpasses the content on feed. and watching white lotus made me miss koh samui sm hence this post 😭
